<li><a href="/wiki/Allmusic" title="Allmusic">Allmusic</a> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/File:Star_full.svg" class="image" title="4/5 stars"><img alt="4/5 stars" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/51/Star_full.svg/11px-Star_full.svg.png" width="11" height="11" border="0" /></a><a href="/wiki/File:Star_full.svg" class="image" title="Star full.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/51/Star_full.svg/11px-Star_full.svg.png" width="11" height="11" border="0" /></a><a href="/wiki/File:Star_full.svg" class="image" title="Star full.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/51/Star_full.svg/11px-Star_full.svg.png" width="11" height="11" border="0" /></a><a href="/wiki/File:Star_full.svg" class="image" title="Star full.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/51/Star_full.svg/11px-Star_full.svg.png" width="11" height="11" border="0" /></a><a href="/wiki/File:Star_empty.svg" class="image" title="Star empty.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/49/Star_empty.svg/11px-Star_empty.svg.png" width="11" height="11" border="0" /></a></span>/<span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/File:Star_full.svg" class="image" title="2.5/5 stars"><img alt="2.5/5 stars" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/51/Star_full.svg/11px-Star_full.svg.png" width="11" height="11" border="0" /></a><a href="/wiki/File:Star_full.svg" class="image" title="Star full.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/51/Star_full.svg/11px-Star_full.svg.png" width="11" height="11" border="0" /></a><a href="/wiki/File:Star_half.svg" class="image" title="Star half.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/81/Star_half.svg/11px-Star_half.svg.png" width="11" height="11" border="0" /></a><a href="/wiki/File:Star_empty.svg" class="image" title="Star empty.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/49/Star_empty.svg/11px-Star_empty.svg.png" width="11" height="11" border="0" /></a><a href="/wiki/File:Star_empty.svg" class="image" title="Star empty.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/49/Star_empty.svg/11px-Star_empty.svg.png" width="11" height="11" border="0" /></a></span> <a href="http://www.allmusic.com/cg/amg.dll?p=amg&amp;sql=43:132571~T0" class="external text" title="http://www.allmusic.com/cg/amg.dll?p=amg&amp;sql=43:132571~T0" rel="nofollow">link</a></li>
